 Y, Qiu Y, Wang J, Liu Y, Wei Y, Sia J, You T, Zhang X, Zhang L |title=Epidemiological and clinical characteristics of 99 cases of 2019 novel coronavirus pneumonia in Wuhan, China: a descriptive study |url=https://www.thelancet.com/journals/lancet/article/PIIS0140-6736(20)30211-7/fulltext |journal=[[The Lancet]] |volume=395 |issue=10223 |pages=507\u2013513 |display-authors = 6 |doi=10.1016/S0140-6736(20)30211-7 |pmid=32007143 |date=15 February 2020 |access-date=9 March 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200131002254/https://www.thelancet.com/journals/lancet/article/PIIS0140-6736(20)30211-7/fulltext |archive-date=31 January 2020 |url-status=live |name-list-format = vanc}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"LancetClinical\">{{Cite journal|vauthors=Huang C, Wang Y, Li X, Ren L, Zhao J, Hu Y, Zhang L, Fan G, Xu J, Gu X, Cheng Z, Yu T, Xia J, Wei Y, Wu W, Xie X, Yin W, Li H, Liu M, Xiao Y, Gao H, Guo L, Xie J, Wang G, Jiang R, Gao Z, Jin Q, Wang J, Can B|display-authors=6|date=15 February 2020|title=Clinical features of patients infected with 2019 novel coronavirus in Wuhan, China|url=https://www.thelancet.com/action/showPdf?pii=S0140-6736%2820%2930183-5|journal=[[The Lancet]]|volume=395|issue=10223|pages=497\u2013506|doi=10.1016/S0140-6736(20)30183-5|pmid=31986264 |name-list-format = vanc}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"LancetNowcasting\">{{cite journal | vauthors = Perlman S | title = Another Decade, Another Coronavirus | journal = [[The New England Journal of Medicine]] | volume = 382 | issue = 8 | pages = 760\u2013762 | date = February 2020 | pmid = 31978944 | doi = 10.1056/NEJMe2001126 |name-list-format = vanc}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Letko22Jan2020\">{{cite journal|vauthors=Letko M, Munster V|title=Functional assessment of cell entry and receptor usage for lineage B \u03b2-coronaviruses, including 2019-nCoV|date=January 2020 |journal=[[bioRxiv]] |type=preprint |doi=10.1101/2020.01.22.915660 |name-list-format = vanc}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"MedVirEvolution\">{{cite journal | vaut