 2014|df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[File:ESP Isabella Catholic Order GC.svg|80px]] || [[Spain]] ||[[Collar (order)|Knight Collar]] of the [[Order of Isabella the Catholic]] || 23 March 2015<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.boe.es/buscar/doc.php?id=BOE-A-2015-3142|title=Royal Decree 211/2015, 23 March |work=BOE Spanish Official Journal}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[File:GRE Order Redeemer 1Class.png|80px]] || [[Greece]] || Grand Cross of the [[Order of the Redeemer]] || 22 October 2015<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.amna.gr/english/article/11738/Hollandes-visit-to-Athens-is-%22a-visit-of-friendship-and-trust%22|title=Hollande arrives in Athens for official visit|work=Athens News Agency - Macedonian Press Agency (ANA-MPA)}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[File:Order Dostik 1kl rib.png|80px]] || [[Kazakhstan]] || [[Order of Friendship (Kazakhstan)|Order of Friendship]], 1st class || 6 November 2015<ref>{{cite web|url=http://en.tengrinews.kz/politics_sub/Nazarbayev-awards-Order-of-Friendship-to-Francois-Hollande-262843/|title=Nazarbayev awards Order of Friendship to Francois Hollande|work=Tengrinews.kz}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[File:ARG Order of the Liberator San Martin - Grand Cross BAR.png|80px]] || [[Argentina]] || Grand Cross of the [[Order of the Liberator General San Mart\u00edn]] || 25 February 2016<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.clarin.com/politica/Toda-Hollande-Juanita-Moyano-Awada_0_1529247209.html|title=Macri awards Order of Libertator General San Martin to Francois Hollande|work=Tengrinews.kz}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[File:Ordre de la reconnaissance centrafricaine - chevalier.svg|80px]] || [[Central African Republic]] || Grand Cross of the Order of Central African recognition || 13 May 2016<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.abangui.com/h/52390.html|title=Fran\u00e7ois Hollande d\u00e9cor\u00e9 \u00e0 la dignit\u00e9 de Grand-croix dans l'ordre national de la reconnaissance centrafricaine|date=15 May 2016|publisher=Bangui.com|accessdate=22 March 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[File:PRT_Order_of_Liberty_-_Grand_Cross_BAR.png|